highlights.text: “Hier Mag Alles” by Donnie and Marco Schuitmaker has been on Top Songs Netherlands the longest, at 592 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Top Songs Netherlands. “Golden” is the highest at #53.
“Positions” by Stryv, Malachiii, and Adam Port is the highest new entry on Top Songs Netherlands at #164.
“Kisses (feat. bbyclose)” by BL3SS, CamrinWatsin, and bbyclose is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Netherlands, up 61 spots at #89.
